    <string name="help_rules">
        <![CDATA[
            <p>
                <br>
                <b>Rules:</b> <br>

                1. Each player is assigned a corner at the beginning of the game. <br>
                2. Players take turns filling their tiles with one of 6 colors in an attempt to capture adjacent tiles of the same color. <br>
                3. You cannot change the color to yours or your opponent\'s. <br>
                4. The game ends when there are no tiles left to capture. <br>
            </p>
            <p>
                <br>
                <b>Goal:</b> <br>

                The goal of the game is to capture more tiles than your opponent, then you win. <br>
            </p>
        ]]>
    </string>
